Tic-Tac-Toe Flow (short notes)
🟢 Main idea
3x3 char board
players take turns (x / o)
loop until win or draw
📌 Functions
-reset_board
called at start / restart
sets all cells to ' '
-print_board
called after every valid move
shows current board
-check_input
called each move
checks range + empty cell
places symbol if valid
-check_win
called after valid move
checks rows, cols, diagonals
returns win / no win
-check_draw
called after check_win
returns draw if no empty cells
🔁 Game flow
1-print board
2-get input
3-validate + place
4-print board
5-check win → stop if true
6-check draw → stop if true
7-switch player
8-repeat
🧩 2D array basics
=board[row][col]
=empty = ' '
=only update ONE cell per move
